{
  "name": "getSiteWxRule",
  "description": "Get Site WxLan Rule Details",
  "parameters": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "site_id": {
        "example": "000000ab-00ab-00ab-00ab-0000000000ab",
        "format": "uuid",
        "type": "string"
      },
      "wxrules_id": {
        "example": "000000ab-00ab-00ab-00ab-0000000000ab",
        "format": "uuid",
        "type": "string"
      }
    },
    "required": [
      "site_id",
      "wxrules_id"
    ]
  },
  "handler": "http",
  "request": {
    "method": "GET",
    "url": {
      "$uri": "https://api.mist.com/api/v1/sites/{site_id}/wxrules/{wxrules_id}"
    }
  },
  "responses": {
    "200": {
      "$encode": "markdown",
      "$block": [
        {
          "$h1": "Object"
        },
        "WXlan",
        "**Key properties:**",
        {
          "$ul": [
            "**action**: type of action, allow / block",
            "**blocked_apps**: blocked apps (always blocking, ignoring action), the key of Get Application List",
            "**created_time**",
            "**dst_allow_wxtags**: tag list to indicate these tags are allowed access",
            "**dst_deny_wxtags**: tag list to indicate these tags are blocked access",
            "**enabled** (default: true)",
            "**for_site**",
            "**id**",
            "**modified_time**",
            "**order**: the order how rules would be looked up, > 0 and bigger order got matched first, -1 means LAST, uniqueness not checked",
            "**org_id**",
            "**site_id**",
            "**src_wxtags**: tag list to determine if this rule would match"
          ]
        },
        {
          "$lang": "json",
          "$code": {
            "$encode": "json",
            "$indent": true,
            "$content": {
              "$": "$.body"
            }
          }
        }
